争夺王冠了。”</p><p>您可以<a href="https://lnk.to/LCAllHell">在此处预订“All Hell”</a> ，并在下面查看完整的曲目列表和专辑封面。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Flos-campesinos-tickets%2Fartist%2F1150053" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>获取 Los Campesinos! 即将到来的美国巡演日期的剩余门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756621" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756621" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756621" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000.jpg" alt="《All Hell》专辑封面。" width="2000" height="1987" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000-400x397.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000-800x795.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000-696x691.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000-1392x1383.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Hell@2000x2000-1068x1061.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756621" class="wp-caption-text"> 《All Hell》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“All Hell”的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“投币断头台”</strong><br /> <strong>2.《圣烟》(2005)</strong><br /> <strong>3.“心灵创伤”</strong><br /> <strong>4. &#39;我。吐;或者，向日葵州形状的咬痕”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“漫长的痛苦”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“语言盛宴”</strong><br /> <strong>7.《季节的顺序》</strong><br /> <strong>8. &#39;二．空中收费站音乐&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>9.《手淫见鬼去》</strong><br /> <strong>10.《小丑之血/奥菲斯》摇头</strong><br /><strong>11.“KMS”</strong><br /> <strong>12. &#39;III.冲浪轨迹”</strong><br /> <strong>13.《月光迷恋》</strong><br /> <strong>14.《0898心痛》</strong><br /> <strong>15.“成人痘印”</strong></p><p>